cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human action recognition from videos using synthetic data and involves techniques such as 3D human body reconstruction and spatio-temporal CNNs. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper involves training models using synthetic data and improving performance on unseen data. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves using synthetic data to improve the performance of a task that requires human-level intelligence. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper involves rendering synthetic videos using 3D human body reconstruction. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with human action recognition from videos and involves techniques such as frame sampling and interpolation.
